author: Inside Edition
description: Model and student Kendall Chrisman from Riverside, California, is living with one of the most inconvenient allergies there is. She noticed her symptoms at 13, when she became itchy and was in pain after every shower. Her symptoms worsened while playing on her college water polo team. After a dermatologist appointment, she learned that she was allergic to water. "It was just the most insane feeling," she told Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall.
title: Model Allergic To Water And All Of Her Bodily Fluids
